  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0db3 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The activist who stole a bed sheet from the presidential palace is remanded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage today (26) ordered that a suspect who was arrested by the Colombo Central Criminal Investigation Unit for stealing a blanket from a bed in the presidential palace be remanded until the 9th.",
        "The police submitted to the court that the suspect had entered the presidential palace with the public on July 9 and it was revealed that a blanket had been stolen from a bed in the presidential palace.",
        "The police have also presented the facts to the court that the suspect was arrested after consulting the CCTV footage and video tapes related to the investigations carried out regarding the incident."
      ],
